milestones.description: Wasim Bari has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (14) for PAK, going past Wasim Raja
Gaekwad and Amarnath's 53-run partnership is IND's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 31 between Engineer and Gaekwad
Amarnath and Vengsarkar's 76-run partnership is IND's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 51 between Ajit Wadekar and Brijesh Patel
Wasim Bari and Sarfraz Nawaz's 27-run partnership is PAK's highest for the 9th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 9 between Saleem Altaf and Sarfraz Nawaz
